<lb n="0473a19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>辟支佛因緣論<note resp="Taisho" n="0473004" place="foot text" type="orig">〔卷上〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0473004" type="mod">卷上【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0473004"><lem wit="【大】">卷上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】 【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
